{"id": 2549, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都见过哪些难以理解的景区审美？", "description": "来说说你旅游时遭受过的视觉冲击，有图晒图。（题图来自：CSA Images ）", "record_count": 5652, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180928175723fEcJY4ypq60LaDsU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 302592, "content": "丽江古城。完全是丽江‘小商品批发市场’城", "image": null, "praise_count": 277, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 302593, "content": "每个城市都有一条名字不同，但卖着都一模一样从义乌批发回来的小商品的特色步行街。", "image": null, "praise_count": 733, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258334}, {"id": 302595, "content": "新修的所谓「步行街」「美食街」——如出一辙…", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417690}, {"id": 302851, "content": "所谓的古文化风景街道都是一排又一排的纪念品店啦，小吃店啦，特产店之类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443037}, {"id": 302597, "content": "无论在哪里，必定有臭豆腐这个选项！", "image": null, "praise_count": 145, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313801}, {"id": 302599, "content": "国庆出游，景点都插满了国旗", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 302602, "content": "非要景区在石头上作画，画奇怪的爱心，把自然的石头涂成五颜六色", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926685}, {"id": 302603, "content": "一些城已经没了住的人，更像一个大市集。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321679}, {"id": 302604, "content": "除了自然风景以外的全部吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 302860, "content": "永垂青史的“xx到此一游”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108007}, {"id": 302605, "content": "刻意而粗糙的仿古砖块和建筑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324195}, {"id": 302606, "content": "溶洞。安几盏七彩灯打到洞壁上，再给各种石头编一些生硬的神话故事，如神龙饮水，仙女下腰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 321, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528931}, {"id": 302862, "content": "不一样的街道和行人，配合着一样的娱乐和消费。和身边的人，一起融入，离开！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450992}, {"id": 302607, "content": "古街道的建设大同小异，都是一些小吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453774}, {"id": 302608, "content": "为啥老是要在大石头上写字？", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696088}, {"id": 311312, "content": "古风建筑牌匾的字从左往右写。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182031}, {"id": 302609, "content": "周庄古镇，完全是卖东西的小市场。竟然还是5A级景区……", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393374}, {"id": 302610, "content": "剪刀手? 标准游客照?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459007}, {"id": 305682, "content": "景区的人人人人人人人人人人人人人人人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477039}, {"id": 302611, "content": "在桂林看到翻修的东西巷和一个古塔，完全就是现代建筑刷红漆，毫无历史感和年代感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464286}, {"id": 305683, "content": "任何雕塑（现代造的）还有周围一大堆硬币\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477039}, {"id": 302612, "content": "搜一下域上和美，就知道什么是下三滥公司，什么是烂俗旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716432}, {"id": 302613, "content": "主打复古风的街道，外表看似质朴，里面依旧充斥着格格不入的商业气息", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717311}, {"id": 302614, "content": "且转移到微博博主“史里芬Schieffen”带你游遍大河北，各种奇观尽览。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717311}, {"id": 302615, "content": "连棕色油漆都还没干，屋子里一股浓浓装修味儿的仿古建筑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427105}, {"id": 302616, "content": "朝着大街的楼体灯金碧辉煌，楼背面一片漆黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460812}, {"id": 302872, "content": "每个学校都有一天爬满藤蔓的长廊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466055}, {"id": 302617, "content": "各地都有、阴魂不散的老酸奶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074638}, {"id": 302618, "content": "中国所有景区卖的东西一模一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 302619, "content": "普通街景却冠上景区。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 303387, "content": "大学校园，图书馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467919}, {"id": 302620, "content": "劣质背景板", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951872}, {"id": 302621, "content": "被摸掉色的雕像", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427107}, {"id": 302622, "content": "今天听同事说，她去了孔雀谷，就俩孔雀，抢其中的工作人员还叫孔雀公主，硬是拉着孔雀尾巴把孔雀送进笼子。\n暴力美学，棒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339512}, {"id": 302623, "content": "一个老头对着雕像尿尿", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464343}, {"id": 302879, "content": "沙县小吃了解一下？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466116}, {"id": 302626, "content": "所有商品/食品/纪念品加上个“老”字就会很高人气", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432426}, {"id": 301092, "content": "瞎胡搞修复后带着浓浓山寨感的艳丽佛像、建筑", "image": null, "praise_count": 415, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302628, "content": "每个古镇都有正宗的长沙臭豆腐是什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469135}, {"id": 302884, "content": "同质化的仿古建筑，一水儿的青砖绿瓦小亭子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443302}, {"id": 301093, "content": "建筑风格混搭中西合璧：古宅门前西洋马车、古镇老街卖星巴克", "image": null, "praise_count": 165, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302629, "content": "新修的类似于古镇的建筑群，也叫古镇吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454775}, {"id": 302885, "content": "把原先有韵味的旧建筑拆掉翻新。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1442337}, {"id": 302630, "content": "图呢？？大家的图呢？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535618}, {"id": 303398, "content": "清河坊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437040}, {"id": 302631, "content": "几间假北欧风式或者俗气少女风的房间凑在一起就成了网红拍照圣地，哪怕甚至是没有任何餐饮休闲娱乐供给。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464396}, {"id": 302634, "content": "景点看不出特色，大部分是炒作出来的，", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431129}, {"id": 302635, "content": "给鬼斧神工或者不鬼斧神工的自然景观加上电梯和玻璃栈道～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873921}, {"id": 302636, "content": "福建省宁德市的牛郎岗沙滩……很小水很脏不知道为什么可以评为3星级的景区……还收门票💰", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464445}, {"id": 302637, "content": "所有的“古镇”都像是批量生产的建筑+一条商业街构成的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152804}]}